# optional secrets. copy to .env (gitignored); the Makefile loads and exports them.
# llm geolocation of news/reddit/tribune text (else a gazetteer fallback). either key
# works — openrouter is tried first (free models, no anthropic spend); the llm only
# names places, a real geocoder (nominatim) then resolves the coordinates.
# (live buses need no key — the frontend pulls them direct from bustimes.org.)
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# sheffield tribune ghost content api key → the tribune layer (read-only, safe to rotate).
TRIBUNE_API_KEY=
